res and is known for its value and reliability',180000,'PearlExportSeries.png'),(30,'TamaImperialstar','drum','The Tama Imperialstar offers a great balance of quality and affordability, featuring durable shells and a wide range of sound options. It’s a popular choice for both beginners and intermediate drummers',125000,'TamaImperialstar.png'),(31,'YamahaStageCustomBirch','drum','The Yamaha Stage Custom Birch is favored for its crisp and clear sound with its birch drum shells. It provides excellent resonance and projection, making it a great choice for live performances and studio recording',130000,'YamahaStageCustomBirch.webp'),(32,'Audio-TechnicaAT2020','mic','The Audio-Technica AT2020 is a versatile condenser microphone known for its clear and detailed sound. It\'s ideal for recording vocals and instruments in both studio and home environments',120000,'Audio-TechnicaAT2020.webp'),(33,'NeumannU87','mic','The Neumann U87 is a legendary studio condenser microphone renowned for its exceptional clarity and warm sound. It\'s a go-to choice for professional vocal recordings and is highly regarded in the industry',130000,'NeumannU87.png'),(34,'RodeNT1-A','mic','The Rode NT1-A is celebrated for its low self-noise and transparent sound quality. It\'s a popular choice for recording vocals and acoustic instruments, offering a clear and detailed sound profile',140000,'RodeNT1-A.jpeg'),(35,'ShureSM58','mic','The Shure SM58 is an industry-standard dynamic microphone known for its durability and reliable performance. It\'s widely used for live vocals and is renowned for its ability to handle high sound pressure levels',128000,'ShureSM58.png'),(36,'ShureSM78','mic','The Shure SM7B is a dynamic microphone famous for its smooth and natural sound, making it ideal for both vocals and broadcasting. Its versatility and built-in shock mount make it a favorite in professional studios',130000,'ShureSM78.png'),(37,'AlesisRecitalPro','electricPiano','The Alesis Recital Pro offers a full-size